text: Propriano () is a commune in the Corse-du-Sud department of France on the island of Corsica. It is situated on the Valinco Gulf. ==Population== 350px == Transport == * Railway stations in Corsica - stillborn branch == See also == * Communes of the Corse-du-Sud department ==References== * INSEE Category:Communes of Corse-du-Sud Category:Corse-du-Sud communes articles needing translation from French Wikipedia
